It takes a village to raise a child. It took a city to grow a star. Aaryaman from Astrix sat with Dhanji - Ahmedabad’s foremost rapper, storyteller and proud local - we explored what it means to develop a culture of authenticity, how fame can be a double edged sword, and why building the right company matters above everything else.

In a special episode of Disclaimer! By Astrix, here’s for the city of Amdavad.
